data.description: "Discover the perfect Hurricane, UT retreat! This fantastic home offers an exceptional location, open floor plan, and a mere 2-minute walk to Hurricane Airport 1L8, with the scenic Hurricane Equestrian Park right behind the subdivision. Nature lovers will relish the convenience of Mollie's Nipple trailhead within walking distance.  Enhanced with freshly painted stucco, this home boasts curb appeal. Positioned conveniently across from the clubhouse, it also comes with low HOA fees, energy-efficient solar panels, and backup battery. Your ideal Utah haven awaits!"
